 sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tSettle<br />\n\tTo settle means to make a decision or an arrangement. What is being settled? How is it settled? Why is it settled?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They finally settled... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) settling a debt<br />\n\t2) settling in a new <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/dwelling\" target=\"_blank\">dwelling</a><br />\n\t3) settling differences<br />\n\t4) sediments settling at the bottom of the river<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tHodge walked towards the door to meet the man entering. After exchanging friendly greetings, with Hodge leading the way, they walked towards a table closer to the back wall. No sooner had they settled down, a server approached them and presented the menu. While Hodge's guest looked through the list of food, the server mentioned the daily special as well as the chef's recommendation. Hodge paid close attention to his guest's reaction, trying to find out his impression of the restaurant. Soon enough, the guest made his decision, and Hodge also decided his meal.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/166530235387/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p761987/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p761987\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764847/\">还我猴王！春晚少了六小龄童 外媒怎么看？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764895/\">猴年来啦！这些猴子短语你都会说吗</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p763700/\">美高校评选年度最讨厌词汇：2016年别再用啦</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764877/\">哥们你忘上色了吗？得了白化病长颈鹿不忧桑</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764917/\">红包照片引爆朋友圈 ：英文表达你会吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764850/\">和外国人神侃想聊星座？快来看看怎么说吧~</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761660/\">27个问题助你找到人生激情</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764956/\">囧研究：灵魂伴侣真的存在吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764964/\">挪威20岁女孩称自己是只喵只是被困于人身……</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p762505/\">10个关于可口可乐不为人知的大秘密</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" sty